         guid=&quot;_3pc9kaDFEeCXF5ZuS3W32Q&quot;>Service innovation workflow&lt;/a>&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul>&#xD;
&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;./resources/atone_default_workflow.png&quot; width=&quot;600&quot; height=&quot;384&quot; />&lt;br />&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    &lt;strong>Figure 1:&lt;/strong> Overview of AT-ONE workflow&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    The practice&amp;nbsp;is developed to be scalable and has been carried out with different numbers of participants and with&#xD;
    workshops lasting between 2 and 5 days. A typical &lt;a class=&quot;elementLink&quot;&#xD;
    href=&quot;./../../../practice.innovation.service_innovation.base-sintef/capabilitypatterns/service_innovation_workflow_5A626264.html&quot;&#xD;
     guid=&quot;_3pc9kaDFEeCXF5ZuS3W32Q&quot;>Service innovation workflow&lt;/a> structure for the complete process with preparations,&#xD;
    workshops and concept-development can be organized as illustrated in figure 1.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
